A little bit about myself...

As an aspiring Full Stack Web Developer,I am looking to dive deeper into the IT industry. I am currently working towards my certificate of completion in full stack web development from the Rutgers’s Coding Bootcamp. With the newly aquired skills in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, JQuery, Node.JS, BootStrap, React.js, responsive web design, and Third Party API's; I look forward to writing and developing user-friendly applications and software. Possessing a solid work ethic, excellent communication skills, I am a strong team player who can work within any department as well as independently. I am comfortable with both Agile and Waterfall methodology as well as being Six Sigma Yellow belt and Scrum Master certified.

I love to learn new things, reading, cooking and spending time outdoors. I am a competitve powerlifter, bodybuilder and strength coach.
